 🚀 FuturePath AI  
### Your Future, Guided by AI

## 🏆 Hackathon Project Submission

FuturePath AI is an AI-powered career guidance platform that helps students and young professionals discover scholarships, internships, and career opportunities based on their personal profile.

Built using an AI-assisted development platform, the system provides a complete end-to-end intelligent career planning experience.
---
## 🎯 Problem Statement
Students today face:
- Lack of proper career guidance  
- Scattered scholarship information  
- Difficulty finding relevant opportunities  
- No personalized roadmap system  
---
## 💡 Our Solution

FuturePath AI solves this by:
- Collecting user profile (skills, interests, education, country)
- Using AI to analyze user data
- Generating personalized opportunities
- Providing career roadmap suggestions
---
## 🧠 AI & Platform
- Built using lovable app
- AI powered by  Gemini  
- Intelligent recommendation system  
- Automated full-stack generation  
---
## 🏗️ Tech Stack
- TypeScript  
- React 19  
- Tailwind CSS  
- Supabase (Auth + Database)  
- Cloud Backend  
- AI Integration (Gemini API)  
---
## ⚙️ Features
- AI Career Recommendations  
- Scholarship Finder  
- Internship Suggestions  
- Personalized Dashboard  
- Roadmap Generator  
- Secure Authentication  
---
## 🚀 Impact
This project helps students turn confusion into clarity by giving them a structured, AI-powered path toward their future.
